<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Página Principal</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg-color: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a40, #0c0c1c);
        --text-color: #ffffff;
        --nav-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        --nav-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        --nav-hover: #6c63ff;
        --button-hover-bg: #836fff;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        background: var(--bg-color);
        color: var(--text-color);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100vh;
      }

      nav {
        background: var(--nav-bg);
        width: 100%;
        padding: 1rem;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-evenly;
        align-items: center;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--nav-border);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      }

      nav a {
        color: var(--text-color);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        transition: color 0.3s;
      }

      nav a:hover {
        color: var(--nav-hover);
      }

      h1 {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        text-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--nav-hover);
      }

      section {
        margin: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav>
      <a href="/register-recipe">Registrar Nueva Receta</a>
      <a href="/recipes/vegetarianas">Vegetarianas</a>
      <a href="/recipes/carnivoras">Carnívoras</a>
      <a href="/recipes/veganas">Veganas</a>
      <a href="/recipes/favoritas">Favoritas</a>
    </nav>
    <h1>Bienvenido a la Página Principal</h1>
    <section>
      <p>Selecciona una opción del menú para comenzar.</p>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>